| Overview             =  The '''Parliament of the United Kingdom''' is the supreme legislative body of the [[United Kingdom]]. It alone possesses legislative supremacy and thereby ultimate power over all other political bodies in the UK and the overseas territories. Parliament is bicameral but has three parts, consisting of the [[Monarchs of Britain|Sovereign]], the [[House of Lords (Earth-616)|House of Lords]], and the [[House of Commons (Earth-616)|House of Commons]]. They all meet at the [[Palace of Westminster]] in the nations capital of [[London (England)|London]].
| History                 = 
[[James Jaspers (Earth-616)|Sir James Jaspers]] MP for West Hanslope grew wary about the growing superhuman threat in the UK. His calls in the House of Commons to deal with the threat almost had him thrown out.{{r|Daredevils Vol 1 7}} He  later won a landslide general election victory becoming [[Prime Minister of the United Kingdom]] due to his Anti-Superhuman stance.{{r|Daredevils #9}}
